erturbation theory which we briefly review\nfor the sake of the reader. Moreover, our method allows us to extend the\nanalysis to certain non-covariant systems having slowly varying magnetic\nfields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2018 17:36:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2020 17:17:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-02"}
