\\geq 2$\nthat the combinatorial generating function $R_n$ is a quantum modular form when\nviewed as a function of $x \\in \\mathbb Q$, where $q=e^{2\\pi i x}$, and the\n$x_j$ are suitable distinct roots of unity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Oct 2018 19:11:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-16"}
